<p><strong><a name="p5"></a>五、定时器</strong></p>
<p>使用 Timer 定时器每天执行一次，下载数据，再刷新画面</p>
<div class="cnblogs_code">
<pre><span style="color: rgba(0, 128, 128, 1)"> 1</span> <span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 255, 1)">def</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)"> start():
</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 128, 128, 1)"> 2</span>     weather=<span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)">Weather()
</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 128, 128, 1)"> 3</span> <span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)">    weather.getPage(url)
</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 128, 128, 1)"> 4</span>     data=<span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)">weather.readPage()
</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 128, 128, 1)"> 5</span> <span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)">    weather.save(data)
</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 128, 128, 1)"> 6</span> <span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)">    display()
</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 128, 128, 1)"> 7</span>     t = threading.Timer(86400<span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)">, start)
</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 128, 128, 1)"> 8</span> <span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)">    t.start()
</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 128, 128, 1)"> 9</span> 
<span style="color: rgba(0, 128, 128, 1)">10</span> url=<span style="color: rgba(128, 0, 0, 1)">'</span><span style="color: rgba(128, 0, 0, 1)">http://www.weather.com.cn/weather1d/101280101.shtml</span><span style="color: rgba(128, 0, 0, 1)">'</span>
<span style="color: rgba(0, 128, 128, 1)">11</span> <span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 255, 1)">if</span> <span style="color: rgba(128, 0, 128, 1)">__name__</span> == <span style="color: rgba(128, 0, 0, 1)">'</span><span style="color: rgba(128, 0, 0, 1)">__main__</span><span style="color: rgba(128, 0, 0, 1)">'</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)">:
</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 128, 128, 1)">12</span>     start()</pre>
</div>
